name: EIR Training Lite
summary:
🏆 Epic Workouts
🎯 BoxFit, Battle Ropes, Pyramid, and much more
💪🏼 All Levels, Beginner to Expert
🚀 Train with Sam & El, our virtual trainers 
🏰 Work Out in Engaging Landscapes
▶️ Compatible with Meta Quest 2, 3, and Pro Headsets
🆓 Free Demo Version, only available on AppLab! 

Strengthen different muscle groups with epic workouts for all fitness levels. Work your upper body with punches, hooks, twists, battle ropes, and dumbbells. Target your lower body with squats, lunges, slams, and footwork....
